title: About
text:
I’m Jacob Jannicelli, a student at Villanova University studying MIS, Business Analytics, and AI / ML.
I’m especially interested in using data and optimization to make better decisions in sports and operations.
Outside of class, I:

Work as Commissioner for Villanova Intramural Sports

Build side projects in R and Python (sports models, scheduling tools, dashboards)

Follow MLB and NBA analytics closely

I’m always open to talking about internships, research, or collaboration.
